WEBVTT

00:10:58.950 --> 00:11:00.612
one idea,

00:11:00.636 --> 00:11:04.298
one innovation can alter an approach,

00:11:04.322 --> 00:11:05.852
change a process

00:11:05.876 --> 00:11:07.770
and even save lives.

00:11:08.599 --> 00:11:12.352
I've been teaching visual intelligence
for over 15 years,

00:11:12.376 --> 00:11:15.592
and to my great amazement
and astonishment --

00:11:15.616 --> 00:11:18.392
to my never-ending astonishment
and amazement,

00:11:18.416 --> 00:11:21.944
I have seen that looking at art
with a critical eye

00:11:21.968 --> 00:11:25.380
can help to anchor us in our world
of uncharted waters,

00:11:25.404 --> 00:11:27.643
whether you are a paramilitary trooper,

00:11:27.667 --> 00:11:30.616
a caregiver, a doctor or a mother.